EDITORS:
</HEADLINE>
  
 Monday, Nov. 9, 1998      The Hearst News Service will file the following stories for
Tuesday. If you have questions, call Tim Spence at 202-298-6920.  
    (Slugline includes the ``HNS'' tag.)
   
