   FBN-MCDONOUGH-COLUMN (Foxborugh, Mass.) -- They thought they
could win, but never like this. By Will McDonough.
</P>
<P>
   FBC-NOTEBOOK (Undated) -- By posting a 28-24 victory over the
Buckeyes in Columbus, the Spartans caused several tremors in
college football. By Mark Blaudschun.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
