   &UR; QUOTABLES FROM NBC'S 'LATE NIGHT WITH CONAN O'BRIEN' &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ``Former wrestler Jesse 'The Body' Ventura was elected as
Minnesota's new governor. This is pretty exciting because he's the
